{"type": "article", "id": 30886, "title": "看看这本丹麦杂志，不爱植物你也能欣赏它们的美", "description": "“我们感受到需要让人们对植物感兴趣，它可以变成一些真正富有诗意和雕塑感的艺术。”", "date": "2016-08-11T23:25:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2443, "name": "杂志"}, {"id": 31377, "name": "blad"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 316, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160811131026yNwflSOHe7kKdCBq.jpeg", "contents": "<p><a href=\"http://www.blad-journal.dk\" rel=\"nofollow\">《BLAD》</a>（丹麦语叶子）是丹麦一本季刊植物杂志，今年夏天他们刚刚发布第五本。</p><p>打开每一页，彩印的高清植物图片让每一丝纹理清晰且充满艺术感，抛开所有的环境或背景，让人安静地欣赏每一株植物。对多数人来说，这些植物都叫不出名字，镜头放大了它们的差别和美，足以赏心悦目地看下去。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131129AaY7HURO8oixSM4K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131604qRJFLNtxXV0gzE3p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131148c0vxM6wWOfFGLTR4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608111319030aFR83xqbHEhk2I4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131848yFWL1JzGvXhw2RsM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131139kbcOgEwqmoPWKVT4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">在生长中的欧洲矮棕 （Chamaerops humilis ）</div></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">《BLAD》是由两位大学同学 Jacobsen and Hotvedt Laursen 一起创办的，她们都是学传媒出身。在做这本杂志时，决心抛弃传统园艺杂志的枯燥和学术，将方向转向都市有机生活，定位于 25 岁到 40 岁的都市人群。<br></p><p>她们邀请到一些年轻的当地的设计师、摄影师、艺术家、作家、插画家一起将植物的生命视为一种艺术形式，发掘一些不常见或被遗忘的植物。“我们感受到需要让人们对植物感兴趣，它可以变成一些真正富有诗意和雕塑感的艺术。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131528NfOP8tM1Ks6XQACn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811132012sId7qGOZQn8AXRUy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Jacobsen and Hotvedt Laursen&nbsp;</div></figcaption></figure></div><p>第一本杂志发布于 2015 年 3 月，在新办的这一本中，她们专注于种子的世界。还有关于鸡尾酒配方和极简日本插花艺术的 DIY 教程。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131940fo3pqK0981NDQdUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131555PNpnVX3SDG76CjKz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131954sglhr3jJLPKIH10Z.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709287\" data-format=\"png\">\n</figure></div><p>为了筹集资金，她们去众筹网站&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/180390847/blad/description\" rel=\"nofollow\">kickstarter </a>中发布了规划，最终 114 位支持者筹集了19055 DKK（19001.8 元）的启动资金。目前已在丹麦、英国、德国、瑞典、意大利和瑞士等地购买。不过杂志使用的还是丹麦语，要是想纯欣赏图片，可以去 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/blad_journal/\" rel=\"nofollow\">instagram</a>&nbsp;上查看。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811131819mNkawI6JOEDpc3yb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811132039iesAmMx1b90IRoqY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612987\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811132200g1d6BURfS7PY5EAG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751892\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160811132327oEX7IiMZL8jblyP3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.736041\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/lifestyle/the-poetry-of-plants-experimental-gardening-magazine-blad-launches-issue-five#166996\" rel=\"nofollow\">wallpaper</a>、<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/blad_journal/\" rel=\"nofollow\">instagram</a>、<a href=\"http://www.blad-journal.dk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">BLAD</a></p>"}